My livejournal IS friends only. But I accept people who actually make an attempt to talk to me (: Here's a basic "About Me"
  • My name is Julia Antoinette
  • I am a senior in High School
  • I transferred to my current school halfway through tenth grade. I still hate it here.
  • Seventeen years old
  • I live in a little town right outside of Philly.
  • I plan on majoring in Communications next year, either at Bloomsburg University or Penn State
  • I want to work on films when i'm older.
  • I have a boyfriend named Johnny. We have been together since April 11, 2008.
  • Even though I am really skinny, I eat like a big fat pig.
  • I dress strangely.
  • One of my hobbies is sewing. I'm not the greatest, but I can do simple things and I have made a few shirts/skirts.
  • Fashion is amazing, i'm obsessed with the old seasons of Project Runway, shopping and magazines.
  • Reading is another one of my hobbies.
  • I write often.
  • My dog is a beagle, his name is Wyatt. He was rescued from a puppy farm when he was only nine or ten months old.
  • When I say I listen to all kinds of music, I mean EVERYTHING.
  • I'm very nice and I have a huge heart.
  • I can be shy.
